.site-div.closed#film-fatales
  p.site-title Film Fatales
  p.site-description Film Fatales is a global network of women filmmakers
  a.site-link href="//filmfatales.org" target="_blank" www.filmfatales.org
  .centering
    a href="//filmfatales.org" target="_blank"
      img.ss.hidden src=image_path("ff.png")
  .site-blurb.hidden
    p The Film Fatales website is built with Ruby on Rails and hosted on Heroku with a postgres database. Film fatales uses an Active Admin CMS interface with bootstrap, sass, javascript, and jquery for the frontend and also utilizes Amazon AWS S3 and Cloudfront services via the Fog gem. Film fatales is monitored via New Relic monitoring services.

